### 1. 註冊管理員帳號
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin User",
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "admin123",
  "role": "admin"
}

### 2. 註冊一般學員帳號
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Student User",
  "email": "student@test.com",
  "password": "student123",
  "role": "student"
}

### 3. 學員登入（取得 Token）
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student@test.com",
  "password": "student123"
}

### 4. Admin 登入（取得 Token）
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 5. 未登入時嘗試查詢（應失敗）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/signup

### 6. 學員建立報名（需替換 TOKEN）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/signup
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_STUDENT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "測試報名",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phone": "0912345678"
}

### 7. 學員查詢自己的報名（只能看到自己的）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/signup
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_STUDENT_TOKEN_HERE

### 8. Admin 查詢所有報名（可以看到全部）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/signup
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 9. 學員嘗試刪除別人的報名（應失敗）
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/signup/PARTICIPANT_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_STUDENT_TOKEN_HERE

### 10. Admin 刪除任何報名（應成功）
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/signup/PARTICIPANT_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
